        content: Or <b>of rich cloth.</b>
      - number: '68:31b '
        content: Hebrew <b>Cush.</b>
    - title: 
      content: 'Sing to God, you kingdoms of the earth.Sing praises to the Lord.
        Interlude  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Sing to the one who rides across the ancient heavens,his mighty voice
        thundering from the sky.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
