      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'They rebelled against the words of God,scorning the counsel of the
        Most High.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'That is why he broke them with hard labor;they fell, and no one was
        there to help them.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201C<smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>, help!\u201D they cried in their
        trouble,and he saved them from their distress.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'He led them from the darkness and deepest gloom;he snapped their
