  - verses:
    - title: 
      content: '  Praise the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>!Praise the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>
        from the heavens!Praise him from the skies!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise him, all his angels!Praise him, all the armies of heaven!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise him, sun and moon!Praise him, all you twinkling stars!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise him, skies above!Praise him, vapors high above the clouds!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Let every created thing give praise to the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>,for
        he issued his command, and they came into being.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'He set them in place forever and ever.His decree will never be revoked.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> from the earth,you creatures
        of the ocean depths,  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'fire and hail, snow and clouds,[[COMMENT(0)]]wind and weather that
        obey him,  '
      comments:
      - number: '148:8 '
        content: Or <b>mist, </b>or <b>smoke.</b>
    - title: 
      content: 'mountains and all hills,fruit trees and all cedars,  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'wild animals and all livestock,small scurrying animals and birds,  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'kings of the earth and all people,rulers and judges of the earth,  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'young men and young women,old men and children.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Let them all praise the name of the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>.For
        his name is very great;his glory towers over the earth and heaven!  '
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - title: 
      content: '  Praise the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>!Sing to the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>
        a new song.Sing his praises in the assembly of the faithful.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'O Israel, rejoice in your Maker.O people of Jerusalem,[[COMMENT(0)]]
        exult in your King.  '
      comments:
      - number: '149:2 '
        content: Hebrew <b>Zion.</b>
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise his name with dancing,accompanied by tambourine and harp.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'For the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> delights in his people;he crowns
        the humble with victory.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Let the faithful rejoice that he honors them.Let them sing for joy
        as they lie on their beds.  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Let the praises of God be in their mouths,and a sharp sword in their
        hands\u2014  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'to execute vengeance on the nationsand punishment on the peoples,  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'to bind their kings with shacklesand their leaders with iron chains,  '
      comments: []
  - verses:
    - title: 
      content: '  Praise the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>!Praise God in his sanctuary;praise
        him in his mighty heaven!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise him for his mighty works;praise his unequaled greatness!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Praise him with a blast of the ram\u2019s horn;praise him with the
        lyre and harp!  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise him with the tambourine and dancing;praise him with strings
        and flutes!  '
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: 'Praise him with a clash of cymbals;praise him with loud clanging
        cymbals.  '
      comments: []
